# GUI Password Generator

## Overview

This project is a simple GUI-based Password Generator developed using Python and Tkinter. It allows users to generate strong and secure random passwords with a single click.

## Features

* Generate secure random passwords
* Simple graphical user interface
* One-click password generation
* Uses letters, numbers, and special characters

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Tkinter

## How to Run

1. Install Python on your system
2. Download or clone the repository
3. Run the following command in terminal:

python gui_password_generator.py

## Project Structure

password-generator-gui
